            <title><![CDATA[中国邮政9月3日将发行黑猫警长邮票]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/0060kcm8ly1h5apucpclgj60u00k90ur02.jpg?VersionId=B.4d3mwapWbtKuoK_xxaBgx9A7lqa4Oq&amp;itok=Q3obCFf4" title="《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票。（取自中国邮政微博）" alt="《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票。（取自中国邮政微博）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/0060kcm8ly1h5apucpclgj60u00k90ur02.jpg?VersionId=B.4d3mwapWbtKuoK_xxaBgx9A7lqa4Oq&amp;itok=Q3obCFf4" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
      <figcaption>《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票。（取自中国邮政微博）</figcaption>
       
            

<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国邮政将在9月3日发行《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据央视新闻报道，《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票一套五枚，计划发行630万套，全套邮票面值5.20元（人民币，约1.06新元）。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据中国邮政官方微博，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>这套邮票由尚盈设计，北京邮票厂有限公司采用影写版工艺印制，色彩明快、饱和度高，并且采用了金、银特种金属墨。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
      

<figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-08/0060kcm8ly1h5apxql211j60xc0m942k02.jpg?VersionId=_GF5Xl0qHNqhlqx1vER_fSRY1DOjJwJ2" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>《动画——黑猫警长》特种邮票采用了金、银特种金属墨。（取自中国邮政微博）</figcaption></figure>                  <p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>这套邮票表现了动画中制服强盗、捉捕恶鹰、保卫家园、并肩作战、大获全胜的故事情节，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>突出展现了黑猫警长英姿飒爽、智勇双全的经典动画形象。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      

<figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-08/0060kcm8ly1h5apu94ocij60u00k0q5m02.jpg?VersionId=qluNG.gV7FOCCY4HkKNX37xZz8vIUZgf" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
